    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with a few minor door dings and scratches typical for its year. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though the air conditioning takes a moment to get cold and there is a small oil drip that doesn't affect performance. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
