    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a total joy to drive and has stayed in really wonderful shape over the years! It runs smoothly and still has that great look that\u2019ll turn heads in the driveway. I\u2019ve genuinely loved owning this beauty, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality ride without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
