    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with its signature high-revving individual throttle bodies. This chassis remains rigid with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed VANOS system for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein B16 dampers for improved turn-in and lateral grip. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for the spirited enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
